<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>Welcome to TodoApp's privacy policy. Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our TodoApp. By using this application, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>While using TodoApp, we may collect the following data:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Task Information:</strong> Task names, descriptions, due dates, and completion status.</li>
    <li><strong>User Metadata:</strong> Timestamps related to task creation, editing, and completion.</li>
</ul>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>We use the collected information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Manage your tasks effectively.</li>
    <li>Provide a history of completed tasks.</li>
    <li>Enhance the performance of the app.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Storage and Security</h3>
<p>Your task data is securely stored in our database, and we use security measures to protect it. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>

<h3>Sharing of Information</h3>
<p>We do not share your data with any third parties. All your task-related information is used only within the TodoApp.</p>

<h3>Your Rights</h3>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Access, edit, or delete your tasks at any time.</li>
    <li>Request the deletion of all your data if you stop using the app.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. You will be notified of any significant changes.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
<p>Email: support@todoapp.com</p>
